{
    "zh-CN": {
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_NAME": "刺客",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_DESCRIPTION": "刺客是一名身手敏捷的远程角色,可以使用毒药对敌人造成持续伤害。<color=#CCD3E0>\n\n< ! > 匕首非常适合对付单个目标。\n\n< ! > 毒药在对付一大群敌人时非常有效。\n\n< ! > 尽管传送术非常强大,但弧线降落意味着要准确降落至目标点并不轻松,因此请瞄准您着陆点的偏上位置。\n\n< ! > 当你激活传送器时,战吼技能将有奇效。\n\n",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_SUBTITLE": "无声蛊毒师",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_LORE": "刺客曾贵为炼金奇才,注定要名垂青史。他们热爱酿造,希望研制出任何想要的药水。得到了前辈的指导之后,他们的炼金技艺变得炉火纯青,最终获得了\"炼金大师\"的称号。然而,随着时间的推移,污秽之物侵蚀了他们的内心,他们开始变得贪婪,这与炼金术士所信奉的\"炼金之道\"背道而驰。最终他们抛弃了炼金术士的身份,离开了土生土长的故土。\n\n贪婪汇聚仇恨,刺客逐渐堕入了他们未曾设想的黑暗道路。随着最后一丝残存的理智也被欲望吞噬,他们陷入了疯狂,开始将自身所学投入更黑暗的目的。他们花费数月时间酿造出自己的\"得意\"作品,一种致命的神经毒素,任何生命在这种毒药面前都显得脆弱不堪。他们知道就连自己也无法在这种毒药中幸存,便制作了解药藏在斗篷中随身携带。\n\n就这样,他们收获了另一个臭名昭著的称号:\"冷酷无情的赏金猎人\"。各路的罪犯和军阀都想方设法的寻找他们的服务,\"毒药暗杀,干脆利落\",已经成为他们的招牌。在强大的炼金基础加持之下,他们陆续研制出其他药水:有的可以移动自身分子结构,还有的可以实现空间传送。\n\n在之前毒药的基础上,他们做了点\"小创造\",研制出毒性更强的毒药。新的毒药能够几乎在瞬间施放全部毒素,副作用是毒素会在空气中停留。\"只需一瓶,就能够收割一整屋人的性命\"。\n\n这一次,他们奉命前往杀死U.S.S.安全旅行号的船长,这是他们有史以来最大的任务,然而在着陆后,他们感到一种强大的超自然力量正将他们引向一条越来越黑暗、越来越深的道路。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_OUTRO_FLAVOR": "..于是他们离开了,去领取一笔不菲的赏金。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_OUTRO_FAILURE": "..于是他们消失了,无影无踪。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_EXPLOSIVEDECOY_NAME": "刺客诱饵",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_KEYWORD_DAGGER_WC": "<style=cKeywordName>强化</style>\n<style=cIsUtility>在战吼施放期间,</style>投掷4把匕首。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_KEYWORD_GHOSTLY_WC": "<style=cKeywordName>强化</style>\n<style=cIsUtility>在战吼施放期间,</style>最低伤害增加至 <style=cIsDamage>75%</style>。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_KEYWORD_POISON_WC": "<style=cKeywordName>强化</style>\n<style=cIsUtility>在战吼施放期间,</style>投掷一簇效果逐渐衰减的毒药。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_KEYWORD_VENOM_WC": "<style=cKeywordName>强化</style>\n<style=cIsUtility>在战吼施放期间,</style>投掷2瓶药水,并在地面上形成一团有毒的扇形区域。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_KEYWORD_TELEPORT_WC": "<style=cKeywordName>强化</style>\n<style=cIsUtility>在战吼施放期间,</style>更快施展传送术,并且在途中施放一团毒雾。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_KEYWORD_ROLL_WC": "<style=cKeywordName>强化</style>\n<style=cIsUtility>在战吼施放期间,</style>翻滚后技能增益与战吼增益叠加。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_KEYWORD_DECOY_WC": "<style=cKeywordName>强化</style>\n<style=cIsUtility>在战吼施放期间,</style>在身后位置留下毒药。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_DEFAULT_SKIN_NAME": "默认",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_MASTERY_SKIN_NAME": "尊贵",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_GRAND_MASTERY_SKIN_NAME": "神圣",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_PASSIVE_NAME": "狂神之怒",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "在生命值低于<style=cIsHealth>60%最大生命值</style>时受到伤害将会增加你的攻速和伤害,<style=cIsDamage>每层+7.5%</style>,持续<style=cIsUtility>3秒</style>。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_ALT_PASSIVE_NAME": "恐惧之毒",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_ALT_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "受到伤害时会向伤害来源方向投掷毒药,造成<style=cIsDamage>250%的伤害</style>,随时间推移增加额外的<style=cIsDamage>500%的伤害</style>。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_ALT1_PASSIVE_NAME": "诡秘之术",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_ALT1_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "受到伤害时有<style=cIsUtility>5%的几率</style>生成一个存活5秒的诱饵,诱饵将会爆炸并造成<style=cIsDamage>1500%的伤害</style>。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_PRIMARY_DAGGER_NAME": "匕首",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_PRIMARY_DAGGER_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>灵巧。</style>投掷2把匕首,造成<style=cIsDamage>100%的伤害</style>。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_PRIMARY_CUTTER_NAME": "幽灵匕首",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_PRIMARY_CUTTER_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>灵巧。</style>投掷1把匕首,造成<style=cIsDamage>30%到200%的随机伤害</style>。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_SECONDARY_POISON_NAME": "毒药",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_SECONDARY_POISON_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>灵巧。</style>投掷毒药,造成<style=cIsDamage>250%的伤害</style>,随时间推移增加额外的<style=cIsDamage>500%的伤害</style>。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_SECONDARY_POISON_DESCRIPTION_SCEPTER": "<style=cIsUtility>灵巧。</style>投掷1瓶浓缩毒药,造成<style=cIsDamage>250%的伤害</style>,随时间推移每瓶药剂增加额外的<style=cIsDamage>500%的伤害</style>。\n\n<style=cKeywordName>在战吼施放期间,投掷一簇效果逐渐衰减的毒药</style>。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_SECONDARY_POISON_NAME_ALT": "烈性毒药",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_SECONDARY_POISON_DESCRIPTION_ALT": "<style=cIsUtility>灵巧。</style>投掷烈性毒药,造成<style=cIsDamage>500%的伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>毒液会持续5秒</style>。<style=cDeath>不会造成中毒效果</style>。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_SCEPTER_SECONDARY_POISON_DESCRIPTION_ALT": "<style=cIsUtility>灵巧。</style>投掷2瓶烈性毒药,呈扇形分布,造成<style=cIsDamage>500%的伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>毒液会持续5秒</style>。<style=cDeath>不会造成中毒效果</style>。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_UTILITY_CLOAK_NAME": "传送术",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_UTILITY_CLOAK_DESCRIPTION": "向准星位置投掷药水,<style=cIsUtility>角色将传送至其落地处</style>,然后向地面投掷药水,<style=cIsUtility>药水将生成一团烟雾,给予角色隐身与速度增益</style>。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_UTILITY_ROLL_NAME": "隐身术",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_UTILITY_ROLL_DESCRIPTION": "向前翻滚,进入隐身状态,并获得小幅移速提升。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_UTILITY_DECOY_NAME": "引诱术",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_UTILITY_DECOY_DESCRIPTION": "向前翻滚,在原位置留下一个即将爆炸的诱饵。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_SPECIAL_POISON_SPAM_NAME": "战吼",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_SPECIAL_POISON_SPAM_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>增加自己和自身所有能力,持续5秒</style>。",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_SPECIAL_BACKSTAB_NAME": "致命穿刺",
        "HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_SPECIAL_BACKSTAB_DESCRIPTION": "刺伤敌人,造成<style=cIsDamage>750%的伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>从背后刺伤普通敌人时</style>,<style=cIsHealth>将立即杀死目标</style>。从背后刺伤BOSS时,有<style=cIsUtility>2%的机率</style><style=cIsHealth>立即杀死目标</style>。否则,对其造成<style=cIsDamage>目标20%生命值的伤害</style>。",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_MASTERYACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Assassin: Mastery",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_MASTERYACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Assassin, beat the game or obliterate on Monsoon or higher.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_GRANDMASTERYACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Assassin: Grand Mastery",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_GRANDMASTERYACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Assassin, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon or higher.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_POISONACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Assassin: Deathly Concoction",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_HASTEREAPR_ASSASSIN_POISONACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Assassin, apply 10 stacks of Assassin's Poison on a single enemy."
